Responsive Design

Responsive design is a fundamental skill that allows websites to adapt and display properly on different devices and screen sizes. It involves using techniques such as fluid grids, flexible images, and media queries to ensure optimal user experience across various devices.

Design Fundamentals

Design fundamentals encompass the core principles and elements of design, including color theory, typography, layout, and composition. Understanding design fundamentals helps create visually appealing and effective designs that communicate effectively and engage the audience.
